Class DBBaseFieldTable

java.lang.Object
  arlut.csd.ganymede.server.DBBaseFieldTable
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<DBObjectBaseField>
public class DBBaseFieldTable
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<DBObjectBaseField>

A customized variant of the java.util.Hashtable class that is tuned for use in managing DBObjectBaseFields in a Ganymede DBObjectBase.

Author:
Jonathan Abbey, jonabbey@arlut.utexas.edu, ARL:UT
